comment: If A025455(n) > 0 then a(n + k^3) > 0 for k>0; a(A119977(n))>0; a(A003072(n))>0. - _Reinhard Zumkeller_, Jun 03 2006

link: Charles R Greathouse IV, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
Index entries for sequences related to sums of cubes
